The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Big W system

London: A system of computer-generated video replays to monitor line calls could be in place at Wimbledon and other major tennis events after the technology was given the thumbs-up by organisers on Friday. The ITF said that the latest version of the Hawk-Eye electronic line calling review system had met the criteria set by a testing committee. (Reuters) 




